701047f-a.title: Bronx: Fieldston Road - Goodridge Avenue
701047f-a.text:
4651 Fieldston Road, west side, south of its junction with Goodridge
Ave., in the restricted residential section known as Fieldston. It is at
this date (1938) the home of Benjamin Winchell.
About 1929.
Brown Brothers.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
